    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a limited-slip variable M differential for optimal corner-exit traction. This chassis has been mechanically maintained with a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed VANOS system, ensuring structural rigidity and timing precision. Riding on a factory-tuned suspension with crisp turn-in response, it remains a benchmark for naturally aspirated performance. Recent service includes a full valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul, making this a turn-key enthusiast machine.",
