    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for 2018 BMW 540i in Alpine White over Mocha Dakota leather. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance for a discerning driver looking for luxury without the showroom price tag. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, having been garage-kept and hand-washed regularly. While there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel, the body is remarkably straight with no major dents or rust. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the leather seats show only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster, and all electronics\u2014from the navigation system to the heated seats\u2014function flawlessly. It has never been smoked in and remains free of odors. Mechanically, this car is sound. It comes with a full-service history including recent oil and filter changes, and the tires have approximately 60% tread remaining. The 3.0L turbocharged inline-six engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp. This is a reliable, high-performance sedan that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
