      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and consistent maintenance. This automobile has been curated for the discerning driver, offering a refined performance profile and a well-preserved interior. Every aspect of this vehicle reflects a commitment to quality, ensuring it remains a reliable and sophisticated choice for its next owner. We invite you to experience the superior standard of this exceptional offering.",
