      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six. This unit boasts a broad powerband thanks to its high-pressure Double-VANOS system and six individual throttle bodies. The chassis remains composed with recent polyurethane bushing upgrades and documented subframe reinforcement. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal traction. While showing honest signs of use, the drivetrain is robust, with rod bearings addressed and a valve clearance adjustment recently performed. A true driver\u2019s specimen for those prioritizing tactile steering feedback and high-revving linear delivery.",
